queries.sql: SELECT DISTINCT d.NID, d.Nama, mk.KdMk, mk.ThnAjaran, m.NmMk FROM matriks mk JOIN dosen d ON mk.KdDosen = d.NID LEFT JOIN matakuliah m ON m.KdMk = mk.KdMK WHERE mk.kdKelas = '300' AND d.NID NOT IN ( SELECT hs.NID FROM hasil hs WHERE hs.NIM = '1502036' AND hs.NID = mk.KdDosen AND hs.KdMatakuliah = mk.KdMk AND hs.TahunAkademik = mk.ThnAjaran )
SELECT k.KdKuisioner, k.pertanyaan, kt.Jenis_Kuisioner FROM kuisioner k JOIN kategori kt ON k.KdKategori = kt.KdKategori WHERE kt.Jenis_Kuisioner = 'Kinerja Dosen'
